item.description:
In this example, we want to sync example.com except &lsquo;example.com/temp_uploads&rsquo;
rsync -avz --exclude 'example.com/temp_uploads' example.com /var/www_backups  NOTE: exclude files are always relative.
details in https://www.thegeekstuff.com/2011/01/rsync-exclude-files-and-folders
